&lt;p&gt;The Environment Artist will be responsible for the design and creation of detailed large-scale full-CG and matte painted environments for live-action and animated features.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will use a flexible generalist approach to your work, but within the context of a mature pipeline with well-defined standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally 4+ years experience making environments for high-end live-action vfx feature films and/or television series.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience on animated feature films or large-scale vfx pipeline preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Environment modelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Natural Environments: landscapes, foliage, rocks &amp;amp; debris, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Urban Environments: background cities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Environment Texturing &amp;amp; Lookdev&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Procedural &amp;amp; painted texturing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generating flow/deposition/erosion/arbitrary masks to modulate texturing/lookdev&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic lookdev setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Environment dressing/layout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scattering tools &amp;amp; manual layout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Matte Painting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Painting/photo collage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-camera projections on geometry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Essential:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Photoshop, Nuke, Maya, Speedtree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Houdini Landscape Tools, Terragen, WorldMachine, Vue or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nice to have:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mari, Substance Designer/Painter, Houdini, Katana/Arnold&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
